property.name: mapreduce.workflow.name
property.value:
select trx1.cs1 As CustID , max(trx1.Trx_Normalized_Datetime) As DateTime , alrt_1.status_id As isFraud , trx1.transaction_key As EREKey , trx1.transaction_type As TxType , trx1.trx_action_cd As TxAction , TRX1.PAYEE_NAME As Payee , TRX1.REQUESTED_AMOUNT_AS_ENTERED As AmtWire , TRX1.SESSION_KEY As CorrID , Res.Custom_Medium_String_03 As IsWireDelayChallenge , trx2.auth_return_cd , trx1.authentication_method1 , trx2.auth_match_ind , trx2.cb68 , trx1.rejected_type_cd
from bdh_raw_ent_risk_engn_ifm.ff_all_transactions_lst_t trx1
left join bdh_raw_ent_risk_engn_ifm.ard_result_policy_rule_lst_t pr --(partition: reference_date) on pr.result_id=trx1.actimize_transaction_key and pr.reference_date=trx1.trx_normalized_date and pr.reference_date =20210406
left join (select * from bdh_raw_ent_risk_engn_ifm.rcm_rules_lst_t rulz --(partition: dw_srce_as_of_dt) where rulz.dw_srce_as_of_dt = 20210406) rulz_1 on pr.rule_id=rulz_1.rule_id
left join bdh_raw_ent_risk_engn_ifm.ard_result_lst_t res --(partition: reference_date) on pr.result_id = res.result_id and pr.reference_date=res.reference_date
left join bdh_raw_ent_risk_engn_ifm.ard_result_alert_relation_lst_t rel --(partition: reference_date) on pr.result_id=rel.result_id and pr.reference_date=rel.reference_date
left join (select * from bdh_raw_ent_risk_engn_ifm.v_rcm_alerts alrt --(partition: dw_srce_as_of_dt) where alrt.dw_srce_as_of_dt = 20210406) alrt_1 on rel.alert_id=alrt_1.alert_id
left join bdh_raw_ent_risk_engn_ifm.ff_all_transactions_2_lst_t trx2 on trx1.actimize_transaction_key=trx2.actimize_transaction_key and trx1.trx_normalized_date=trx2.trx_normalized_date and trx1.trx_normalized_datetime >= '2021-04-06 00:00:00' and trx1.trx_normalized_datetime < '2021-04-07 00:00:00'
where 1=1 and trx1.trx_normalized_date = 20210406 and trx1.trx_normalized_datetime >= '2021-04-06 00:00:00' and trx1.trx_normalized_datetime < '2021-04-07 00:00:00' and trx1.transaction_type = "WIRE"
group by trx1.cs1 , alrt_1.status_id , trx1.transaction_key , trx1.transaction_type , trx1.trx_action_cd , TRX1.PAYEE_NAME , TRX1.REQUESTED_AMOUNT_AS_ENTERED , TRX1.SESSION_KEY , Res.Custom_Medium_String_03 , trx2.auth_return_cd , trx1.authentication_method1 , trx2.auth_match_ind , trx2.cb68 , trx1.rejected_type_cd
